Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.Interface.Employee.model.Employee

  • @Entity(name="emp")
public class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the Employee Component model, and all it's properties which are six: emp_id, emp_name, emp_email, emp_pos, emp_phone, emp_salary and dep
